Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.62,0:22:31.83,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}請你不要視而不見
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.83,0:22:36.63,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}我們不再是乳臭未乾的小孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.63,0:22:40.88,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}即便是扮家家酒我也想知道
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.88,0:22:45.59,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}只有一半已經不能滿足
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.59,0:22:55.40,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}啊 沒有預感 沒有答案
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.40,0:22:58.90,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}試著踮起腳尖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.90,0:23:03.49,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(0,640)\blur4}因為我想離你更近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:06.78,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}曖昧不清 無法割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:12.33,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你的態度令我焦慮不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:15.42,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}難以平復
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:21.09,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}眨眼間也是想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:24.22,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想讓你回頭看向我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:29.76,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天也對著鏡子暗暗發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:33.06,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感覺鬱鬱寡歡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:39.44,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,360)\blur4}你在我心中 魂牽夢縈
